{
  "prompt": "A mystical celestial body floating in space, known as Lilareyvon IX. The planet has a smooth mineral-ceramic surface, glowing in soft violet-black with golden geometric lattice patterns beneath its skin. Orbiting the planet are fragmented, floating glyph-plates that shimmer like ancient runes. At the top and bottom poles of the planet are trinary spiral portals, glowing faintly and emitting subtle anti-gravity pulses. A deep diagonal crack scars across the planet, glowing faint gold, signifying a place of mythic entry. The background is a dreamlike starfield, with misty hues of blue and violet surrounding the planet like an atmosphere of dreammist.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A powerful magical sigil designed for Zero-Drag Convergence. The sigil is glowing with soft golden and violet light, etched into a dark obsidian-like circular tablet. Its design features three interlocking spirals at the core, surrounded by geometric lines, mirrored glyphs, and celestial markings. Around the outer rim are ancient runes representing anti-gravity pulses and unity of dual energies. The background is deep cosmic space, giving the sigil an aura of sacred purpose and infinite energy.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
